Method.СоздатьНаборЗаписейРегистраИзСтруктуры.Description=Fills a register record set from a structure\nSetRecords           - InformationRegisterRecordSet  - Register record set to fill\nStructureObject      - Structure                     - Data for filling the object\n*Filter           - Structure                   - Description of the register record filter\n**<field name>   - Arbitrary                   - Filter value\n*Records          - Array(Structure)            - Array of register records\n**<field name>   - Arbitrary                   - Values of dimensions, resources and attributes of a register record\nGetBrokenRef         - Boolean                       - True - if the object referenced does not exist,\na broken reference will be returned;\nFalse - an empty reference will be returned\nListProperties       - String                        - List of allowed properties\nArray of String                (if empty, all properties are allowed)\nExcludingProperty    - String                        - List of excluded properties\nArray of String                (if empty, all properties are allowed)
